messages.message: After quite a bit more testing - it seems the LLM sees and understands the checkboxes fine - but there is an OCR issue in aligning the checkboxes with titles (see prompt sequence below). Is there something we can do here? Checkboxes feature on a lot of insurance forms, and would be a huge use case.
checkbox improvements are coming in 23.08. @Bas -- can you share your docs for the team to add to their benchmark dataset? cc @Hari
@Kerry @Hari This would be a good benchmark form. It is an acord form for US commercial submissions would be the most popular form for one our most popular use cases
